Package: gamInflu
Type: Package
Title: Influence Analysis for Generalized Additive Models
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Your Name
Maintainer: Your Name <your.email@example.com>
Description: Provides comprehensive influence analysis for Generalized Additive Models (GAMs) 
    fitted with mgcv. Supports all smoother types including s(), te(), ti(), t2(), and by= terms.
    Generates step plots, influence plots, and coefficient-distribution-influence (CDI) plots
    to understand model structure and term influence.
